title: Week 9 Recap, Zeke Plays In Cowboys Win, Brawls In Jax/NO (Football 11/06)
description:
Nick Kostos, Pete Prisco, Will Brinson and Jason La Canfora discuss Zeke Elliott's impact in the Cowboys victory over the Chiefs, the Falcons missed opportunities and Cam Newton on the ground as the Panthers improve to 6-3, and an impressive Redskins performance in Seattle. The guys also cover dominating offensive outputs by the Eagles against the Broncos, and Rams against the Giants. Nick, Pete, Will and Jason hit on fights in Bucs-Saints, Jags-Bengals, and what to make of the AFC South.
